        pricing_overview: '<p>Playground AI operates on a highly popular Freemium model. The foundational Free tier is incredibly generous, allowing users to generate hundreds of standard-resolution images per day. A monthly "Pro" subscription is required for massive power users, unlocking faster generation speeds on premium GPUs, higher resolution upscaling, priority access during peak hours, and strict commercial privacy modes.</p>',
        comparison_summary: '<p>Playground AI sits comfortably between Midjourney and Adobe Photoshop. Midjourney provides the best raw aesthetics in the world but zero editing control. Photoshop provides absolute editing control but requires professional skill. Playground AI differentiates itself as the ultimate *Prosumer Sandbox*. It takes the chaotic, overwhelming power of open-source Stable Diffusion and wraps it in a beautiful, highly intuitive browser canvas, making it the perfect tool for an amateur artist who wants to actively "build" an image rather than just prompting a bot.</p>'
