        pros: ['The true "URL-to-Video" pipeline is a massive revenue driver for e-commerce, allowing shop owners to generate video ads for thousands of specific SKUs automatically without ever picking up a camera', 'Collapsing Canva, ChatGPT, and Hootsuite into a single browser tab drastically accelerates workflow for agencies managing highly demanding clients', 'The automated Carousel generation is brilliant for LinkedIn thought-leadership, turning a boring text block into an engaging slide-deck instantly', 'The built-in competitor analysis actually provides data-driven intelligence on *what* to generate, rather than forcing the user to guess what content will work'],
