        pricing_overview: '<p>Predis.ai operates on a tiered SaaS subscription architecture, heavily scaled by usage limits. The "Solo" tier provides limited monthly generated posts and covers single active brands. The larger "Agency" tiers aggressively expand the limits, unlocking dozens of distinct workspaces, massive API generation limits, white-labeling features, and multi-user collaboration.</p>',
        comparison_summary: '<p>Predis.ai competes in the aggressive "All-in-One Generator" market against Ocoya, Simplified, and Canva\'s growing AI suite. Canva is the undisputed king of manual design. Ocoya focuses heavily on sheer velocity and standard graphic/text combinations. Predis.ai differentiates itself through its deep, specific obsession with *Automated Video & E-commerce Integration*. It acts as the ultimate robotic videographer for Shopify owners, explicitly designed to bridge the terrifying gap between a static product catalog and the hyper-demanding algorithm of TikTok.</p>'
